										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><b>Launched in October 2022</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, Decentrawood is an AI-powered Web3 entertainment ecosystem that combines gaming, intelligent AI, the metaverse, social experiences, and digital ownership into a unified platform. With the launch of </span><b>DEOD AI</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, the ecosystem has expanded to enable users to create, verify, deploy, and use autonomous AI agents for real-world automation and personalized digital experiences. Powered by the </span><b>DEOD</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> token, Decentrawood continues to expand its ecosystem by integrating AI, blockchain technology, and Web3 entertainment into a single decentralized platform. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The project is also rapidly expanding its exchange presence, with </span><b>DEOD set to list on BingX on August 7, 2026</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, while consistently securing new exchange listings almost every month to improve accessibility and liquidity for its growing global community. </span></p>
<h2><b>What is Decentrawood?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Decentrawood is an AI-powered Web3 entertainment ecosystem designed to redefine how people play, create, connect, and earn in the digital world. Built on blockchain technology, it brings together immersive gaming, autonomous AI, the metaverse, social experiences, a decentralized marketplace, and token-powered rewards into one seamless platform.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">At the heart of the ecosystem is </span><b>DEOD AI</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, enabling users to create, verify, deploy, and use intelligent AI agents for real-world automation and personalized digital experiences. Whether you&#8217;re a gamer, creator, developer, or Web3 enthusiast, Decentrawood provides the tools and infrastructure to explore the future of decentralized entertainment.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Powered by the </span><b>DEOD</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> token, every interaction across the ecosystem unlocks new opportunities—from playing games and staking tokens to using AI agents, trading digital assets, and participating in community-driven experiences. Decentrawood is building a future where entertainment, artificial intelligence, and blockchain work together to create a smarter, more rewarding digital economy.</span></p>
<h2><b>DEOD Price Prediction: How Do VentureBurn Experts Analyze It?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">VentureBurn&#8217;s DEOD price predictions are based on both technical analysis and market fundamentals. The team studies historical price trends, trading volume, market sentiment, and key technical indicators such as RSI, MACD, support and resistance levels, trendlines, Fibonacci retracements, and momentum signals to identify potential price movements.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To improve the reliability of its forecasts, VentureBurn combines AI-powered analysis with insights from experienced market analysts. These predictions are shared for educational and informational purposes only and should not be considered financial advice. Always do your own research (DYOR) before making any investment decision.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The analysis also considers broader market conditions. Factors such as increased institutional interest, improving investor sentiment, and supportive macroeconomic developments can drive additional capital into the cryptocurrency market, potentially benefiting promising projects like DEOD.</span></p>
<h3><b>Market Analysis</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The crypto market continues to show strong long-term growth potential as investor confidence and blockchain adoption increase. Projects with real utility and active development are attracting the most attention.</span></p>
<p><b>DEOD</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is one of those projects. With the successful launch of </span><b>DEOD AI</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, Decentrawood has expanded from a Web3 entertainment platform into an </span><b>Agentic AI ecosystem</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, allowing users to create, verify, deploy, and monetize AI agents.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Combined with </span><b>live staking, multiple exchange listings, and a growing community</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, DEOD continues to strengthen its ecosystem. These developments could support long-term growth as AI and Web3 remain two of the fastest-growing sectors in crypto.</span></p>
<h2><b>DEOD Fundamental Analysis</b></h2>
<div id="attachment_203694" style="width: 522px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203694" class="wp-image-203694 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/oavb22720261.jpg" alt="DEOD Fundamental Analysis" width="512" height="246" /><p id="caption-attachment-203694" class="wp-caption-text">Image from DEOD</p></div>
<h3><b>Tokenomics</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">DEOD operates on the upgraded </span><b>Deod v2</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> contract on BNB Chain with a maximum supply of </span><b>1.89 billion tokens</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. The token economy is designed for long-term sustainability rather than short-term inflation. A large portion of the supply is allocated to staking, liquidity, ecosystem growth, DAO initiatives, and long-term vesting, helping reduce immediate selling pressure while supporting future expansion. This structure aligns token distribution with the project&#8217;s long-term roadmap and community growth.</span></p>
<h3><b>Technology Innovation</b></h3>
